集"},{"pid":"cc1966df22d6d8e7a275efcd953fced0e63e6bc9","tid":1886172,"uid":28129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"未去到憎 但覺得佢好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac3038cecd50e42e7d50e8f5d995ff75e129066","tid":1886172,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T23:49:38.000Z","msg":"想佢比武漢佬中出"},{"pid":"5056d627cd0d64579337ae9a44172a5cb920aa51","tid":1886172,"uid":48492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"以前好想留鬚<br />\n但因為舊老細係鬍鬚佬<br />\n依家點都會剃乾淨<br />\n<br />\n幫佢做野嗰陣日日都睇交通新聞<br />\n睇有無佢款車有無車禍<br />\n<br />\n以前上上份明明好單純咁<br />\n上司話點就點<br />\n但到上一份工就係咁睇勞工法<br />\n想搵機會告佢<br />\n<br />\n最近知佢老豆住嗰度有武漢肺炎，想佢中招"},{"pid":"77d60acb099fa4146a7898ea2cdd7cf7b0472bc1","tid":1886172,"uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"無感覺, 睇錢啫, 唔使咁上心嘅"},{"pid":"60f575dc5947fd709b7b71984b508e97e51dd009","tid":1886172,"uid":345689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:54:20.000Z","msg":"個仆街老細將佢條o靚啲嘢隊俾我做，做完大大力掟俾佢<br />\n佢屈我做錯嘢做漏嘢當眾鬧，我完全唔俾反應佢<br />\n日日同個同事圍爐屌9佢，鬼唔望佢快啲收皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條八婆年紀做得我老母但仲成日發老姣，真係諗起都打冷震 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過發夢屌到佢反艇，喊住走，而事實上我都真係激到佢喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我繞過佢直接遞信俾hr<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}